# ikeSecurityAssociationParameters

**Instance Property**

An [doc://com.apple.networkextension/documentation/NetworkExtension/NEVPNIKEv2SecurityAssociationParameters] object containing the parameters for the initial IKE security association to be negotiated with the IKEv2 server.

## Declaration

```swift
var ikeSecurityAssociationParameters: NEVPNIKEv2SecurityAssociationParameters { get }
```

## Accessing IKEv2 Security Association parameters

- **childSecurityAssociationParameters**: An [doc://com.apple.networkextension/documentation/NetworkExtension/NEVPNIKEv2SecurityAssociationParameters] object containing the parameters for the child IPSec security associations to be negotiated for each IKEv2 policy.
- **NEVPNIKEv2SecurityAssociationParameters**: Parameters for an IKEv2 Security Association.
